 of experience working in public health technology.<\\/p>\\r\\n<p style=\\\"font-size: 18pt; line-height: 20pt;\\\">\\u00a0<\\/p>\\r\\n<p style=\\\"font-size: 18pt; line-height: 20pt;\\\"><b>Jyri Soppela | <\\/b>Holds an MSc in bioinformation technology from Aalto University, Helsinki, Finland. Has previously worked as an analyst for several health care companies. He has three years of experience working in public health technology.<\\/p>\\r\\n<p style=\\\"font-size: 18pt; line-height: 20pt;\\\">\\u00a0<\\/p>\\r\\n<p style=\\\"font-size: 18pt; line-height: 20pt;\\\"><b>Mikolaj Kundegorski | <\\/b>Holds an Msc in Computational Software Engineering from Cranfield University. Worked as a research associate in computer vision at Durham University. Two years experience in public health technology.<\\/p>\\r\\n<p style=\\\"font-size: 18pt; line-height: 20pt;\\\">\\u00a0<\\/p>\\r\\n<p style=\\\"font-size: 18pt; line-height: 20pt;\\\"><b>Tomasz Sabala |<\\/b> Msc in Theoretical Physics from Jagiellonian University, Krakow, Poland. Extensive experience in software engineering and management across multiple software companies. One year of experience in public health technology.<\\/p>\",\"fulltext\":\"\",\"state\":1,\"catid\":\"2\",\"created\":\"2018-05-22 09:30:23\",\"created_by\":\"245\",\"created_by_alias\":\"\",\"modified\":\"2018-06-20 13:30:43\",\"modified_by\":\"245\",\"checked_out\":\"245\",\"checked_out_time\":\"2018-06-20 13:30:23\",\"publish_up\":\"2018-05-22 09:30:23\",\"publish_down\":\"0000-00-00 00:00:00\",\"images\":\"{\\\"image_intro\\\":\\\"images\\\\\\/headers\\\\\\/mountains3.png\\\",\\\"float_intro\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"image_intro_alt\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"image_intro_caption\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"image_fulltext\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"float_fulltext\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"image_fulltext_alt\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"image_fulltext_caption\\\":\\\"\\\"}\",\"urls\":\"{\\\"urla\\\":false,\\\"urlatext\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"targeta\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"urlb\\\":false,\\\"urlbtext\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"targetb\